index 2db769f..5a50b4e 100644
--- a/CHANGES.rst
+++ b/CHANGES.rst
@@ -62,6 +62,10 @@ Unreleased
 -   Contexts created during shell completion are closed properly, fixing
     ``ResourceWarning``s when using ``click.File``. :issue:`2644` :pr:`2800`
     :pr:`2767`
+-   ``click.edit()``'s ``filename`` parameter can be an iterable of filenames
+    to open multiple files at once in editors that support it.
+-   Add a ``process_priority`` parameter to ``click.edit()`` to control the
+    CPU priority of the spawned editor process.
 
 
 Version 8.1.8
